fields.title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild
fields.description: An open-world action-adventure game where players explore the kingdom of Hyrule.

fields.title: Super Mario Odyssey
fields.description: A platform game where Mario travels across various worlds to rescue Princess Peach from Bowser.

fields.title: Minecraft
fields.description: A sandbox game where players can build and explore their own worlds made of blocks.

fields.title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt
fields.description: An action RPG where players control Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter searching for his adopted daughter.

fields.title: Red Dead Redemption 2
fields.description: An action-adventure game set in the Wild West, following the story of Arthur Morgan.

fields.title: Fortnite
fields.description: A battle royale game where players fight to be the last one standing.

fields.title: Overwatch
fields.description: A team-based multiplayer first-person shooter where players choose from a roster of heroes.

fields.title: God of War
fields.description: An action-adventure game following Kratos and his son Atreus on a journey through Norse mythology.

fields.title: Cyberpunk 2077
fields.description: An open-world RPG set in a dystopian future where players control V, a mercenary.

fields.title: Animal Crossing: New Horizons
fields.description: A life simulation game where players develop a deserted island into a community of anthropomorphic animals.
